{"tid":1567542,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"連儂牆 撕一貼億","createTime":"2019-09-14T06:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T14:30:34.000Z","uid":181521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"afef5a9107c03fc7ecda1f838b5f56d344f2c4ae","tid":1567542,"uid":181521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:11:29.000Z","msg":"撕就由得佢撕，你得一條友就唔好去阻止，影相都搵返個安全位置，唔使去阻止佢，佢撕仲好，順便可以update最新文宣，但係郁手就要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>打撚鳩柒佢</strong></span></span>，唔好姑息養奸，之前天水圍俾人撕到渣都冇，咪又係起返出嚟，仲要靚過之前，所以佢哋組隊派錢一直撕，我就會一直貼，我就睇吓邊個成本大啲<br />\n<br />\n最好有遊行/行動一人一張文宣順手經過貼埋，達到效果最大化<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今日2點天水圍遊行<br />\n聽日2點銅鑼灣見</strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"275397420b0e6ea064ae0a70d3b4db35988e265f","tid":1567542,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:11:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0a8fca6e30ff3ee62886bd182819ba0c631f2b7","tid":1567542,"uid":320472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:30:34.000Z","msg":"小心依班人清場...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/youthcleaning\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F